For the emerald cut specifically, F-VS1 is the superior specification — F color is one grade better than G (more important in emerald cuts due to color concentration) and VS1 is the minimum safe clarity. Choosing between these two stones should be driven by the GIA certificate's proportion data, not by the $10 price difference.

